description:
"Any artist of any half way reasonable meaning has got to arrive at the place where he does exactly what he wants to do and whether people like it or not should be irrelevant."

Interview with Artie Shaw from the Robert Williams documentary "Mr. Bitchin'"
title: Artie Shaw on art and artists
